revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Sector_CopyScroller}} {{Special|58|tag, flags|Sector|use=line}}
Causes the line's front sector to copy the scroll effect from a tagged sector. * ''tag'': The tag of the sector from which to copy the scroll effect * ''flags'': Which parts of the sector to affect. This can be a combination of the following values: :*1: copy a ceiling scroller :*2: copy a floor scroller :*4: copy a carrying effect
== Conversions from linedef types == The following Doom map format types can be converted as Sector_CopyScroller: {| {{prettytable}} !Type!!Conversion!!Trigger |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 352 || Sector_CopyScroller (tag, 1) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 353 || Sector_CopyScroller (tag, 2) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 354 || Sector_CopyScroller (tag, 6) || |}
